title: How to get European maps for Garmin Mobile XT v4.10.80
description:
Want all European maps for your Garmin_Mobile_XT_v4.10.80 working on for example an N95 8GB?

1. If you have not yet installed Garmin XT on your mobile download this torrent: <a href="
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4138348/UPDATED_Garmin_Mobile_XT_v4.10.80_UK_-_Route66_TomTom_Alt." rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4138348/UPDATED_Garmin_Mobile_XT_v4.10.80_UK_-_Route66_TomTom_Alt.</a>


And follow the complete Readme.PDF. When you're done you'll have only the UK/Ireland map.

2. For the European maps follow the instructions stated on this site: <a href="
http://www.gpsunderground.com/forums/showthread.php?t=1151" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.gpsunderground.com/forums/showthread.php?t=1151</a>

Instructions also listed below (nrs 3-5):

3. At the site of Garmin has several maps to download. But are exclusive to the browser's Samsung.
   But if you open the files.Exe with the program Winrar can get the file GMAPSUPP.IMG!
   I put the file GMAPSUPP.IMG in my sd card (Over the UKmap) and it worked perfectly...

4. Get to this Garmin site to get the maps: <a href=" http://www.garmin.com/garmin/cms/site/us/cache/offonce/us/samsung/overview#fragment-3" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.garmin.com/garmin/cms/site/us/cache/offonce/us/samsung/overview#fragment-3</a>


Download---> open with winrar --->
remove the file GMAPSUPP.IMG (is in the folder called img)--->
Copy it on you SD Card or N95 8G (with necessary file .UNL with the key)
These maps all use mapID 284  
Don't know how to generate an .UNL file? Chec the readme in the torrent listed by step 1.

5. When copying is done deconnect the phone or insert the SDcard into your phone and it should work.


Maps Available: (all for installation on SD card or phine memory)

City Navigator NT, Europe
City Navigator NT, UK & Ireland
City Navigator NT, Italy & Greece
City Navigator NT, DACH & Czech
City Navigator NT, Spain & Portugal
City Navigator NT, Alps
City Navigator NT, France & BeNeLux
City Navigator NT, Nordics
City Navigator NT, Eastern Europe, Austria & Greece
City Navigator NT, Russia
City Navigator NT, Brazil
City Navigator NT, Mexico

All with Map ID: 284 (except for Russia, Map ID: 323) (IDs of South american lands unknown to me)



Good luck!
